<p class="ql-align-center">民警发现篮子里除了自制冰粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还附有花和小纸条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上面写着：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“盆、杯子、篮子，我明天来拿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你们辛苦啦”</strong></p>
